data.title: Daniel Miller (1845
data.text:
H1 Abraham "Abram" Miller, born 20 Oct 1875 in Darke County, Ohio, died 4 Mar 1953, married (1) September 24, 1899, Mary Ellen Good, born 11 Jan 1874, died 9 Mar 1904 Bow Bells North Dakota; married (2) ca. 1908 Williams County, North Dakota, Eva Eikenberry, born ca. 1875 Ohio, died August 16, 1943; ordained an Elder in May 1919, withdrew from the Church of the Brethren in 1926 at the formation of the Pleasant Ridge Dunkard Brethren Church near West Unity Ohio.

H2 Cora Miller, born 8 Oct 1877 in Darke County, Ohio,, married Jacob A. Beckoned, born 13 Feb 1871 near Silver Lake Indiana; s/o Jonas Beckoned & (2) Marilla Flowers. Last known living Anderson, Indiana.

H3 Mary Elizabeth Miller, born 23 Dec 1879 in Darke County, Ohio,, died 7 March 1892.

H4 Isaac Miller, born 4 April 1882 in Darke County, Ohio,.
